race.comment: The maidens kick us off. DRAGON LINK (2) was well supported at Doomben on debut but didn't measure up on that occasion. Was then tipped out for time to furnish and has since revved up for this with a dominant trial win. Where there's smoke there's fire and he can run a big race while fresh. KHOIRGIRL (3) is unlucky to still be a maiden hitting the top-four in all three starts to date. Gets 1.5kg off from the favourable draw and can make her presence felt. CERETTI (7) has placed two of three overall and must be respected out of the Gollan yard. Top-three credentials again. DON'TCHA LUV'ER (8) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown ability at the trials and is sure to be well-educated out of the Bruce stable. Keep very safe. VIOLACEOUS (10) best of the rest.
